{"tid":128340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求助]返PT遇到臭閪主管可以點算？","createTime":"2017-02-20T17:17:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T14:50:03.000Z","uid":85912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8b58ef1d123eada59e2c92c6625131cbceafb3","tid":128340,"uid":85912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:17:08.000Z","msg":"如題 份工返左4個月左右 做得幾開心下 最近超好人嘅大經理因公司人事調動調左去其他鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後有個好撚黑人僧嘅Full time 港女就咁升左做主管呢個位 <br />\n平時份人已經乜都煩鳩住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜春都渣正黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日chur住啲Pt跑數<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前大經理都未叫我啲班Pt追數 你條臭閪憑咩chur我地呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己本身知道大經理就走就已經準備辭職唔做<br />\n奈何大經理同我講話鋪頭真係唔夠人 叫我唔好辭職住 就算一兩粒鐘都照幫手返 咁既然大經理開到口 我絕對唔會say no  放學之後就即刻趕過黎開一或兩個鐘工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後先返屋企食飯溫書<br />\n<br />\n好啦 之後條傻閪港女以為自己做左主管好撚巴閉咁 係咁屌鳩我有冇心返工 你老母冇心嘅就唔會同你返個一兩個鐘工啦晒時間晒車費啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />貪你個八十蚊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n點貨點得慢俾人屌話Hea住黎做 無心返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我點得快就坐左你個位啦on9<br />\n仲叫我呢幾日都唔使翻工 鋪頭夠人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當我係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以點算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：學生一個 做事比較大意 但已經盡力去做"},{"pid":"848776526cda78305b3744923dc0e90211310a97","tid":128340,"uid":76242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"叫佢唔好食咁多大蒜 蔥 果d重味道既調味料<br />\n<br />\n同埋叫佢日日清洗下體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c230584b4b458db34c675c28935fa5097b473e","tid":128340,"uid":85912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫佢唔好食咁多大蒜 蔥 果d重味道既調味料<br />\n<br />\n同埋叫佢日日清洗下體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我認真架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做到好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052b6358aa8d0faba8f5ab12a96599a67d5e4e73","tid":128340,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:28:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫佢唔好食咁多大蒜 蔥 果d重味道既調味料<br />\n<br />\n同埋叫佢日日清洗下體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d1767d430ee3b7dd7dc5a5c2c2552218fc6c8a","tid":128340,"uid":76242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:28:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫佢唔好食咁多大蒜 蔥 果d重味道既調味料<br />\n<br />\n同埋叫佢日日清洗下體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我認真架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做到好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src